Package: algaware
Title: Interactive IFCB Phytoplankton Reporting Tool
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Anders", "Torstensson", , "anders.torstensson@smhi.se", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A Shiny application for processing, validating, and reporting
    phytoplankton data from Imaging FlowCytobot (IFCB) instruments. Integrates
    with IFCB Dashboard for data retrieval, supports interactive validation of
    classifier predictions, and generates Word reports with biomass plots,
    heatmaps, and image mosaics.
